1.0.0 - "Bare Bones"
====================

Basic features for mind map editing.

New features:

* Easy-to-use UI
* Zoom with mouse wheel
* Nice animations
* Save/load in XML-based .ALZ-files
* Full undo/redo
* Zoom in/out/fit
* Quickly add node text and edge labels
* Node color and background color settings

